        <abstract>
            <p>LA clarifies his opposition to CD’s views, which does not blind him to the great value of CD’s original researches.</p> 
<p>Answers CD’s questions regarding sexual coloration of Amazonian fishes and the protuberances on the head of male <hi rend="italic">Geophagus</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Cichla</hi> during the spawning season [see <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>, pp. 520, 529].</p> 
        </abstract>
